\b\fs28 Description:\par
\b0\fs22\par
\fs24 Just recently I happened to learn about a small hammerite outpost where precious ore used to be digged up until not long ago. Unfortunately most of the ore resources are exhausted by now, but since the death of sergeant Cutley's father I suspect some treasures there which are no longer needed. The route leads through an old underground city from which little else should be left then a few walls. Cutley's father used to travel quite a lot and probably brought a couple of treasures into his possession. Among them is an old artifact which he was known to always keep along with him and that he took into his grave. That would be the perfect bauble for one of my fences, wouldn't it? But there is something that catches my interest even more: an old globe. Only this specific globe indicates a secret island where there is believed to be a very big treasure . . . which has never been found so far. Cutley himself is not much of an adventurer and is starting to evacuate the outpost. The few guards which are still left should not be much of a problem . . . and if I want to seek what Cutley's father has not been able to find, then the globe MUST find it's way into my hands!\par
